a-16-person-panel-investigating-ufos-084041440.html">成立了一个单独的小组</a>来调查这一现象。国防部还于 2022 年创建了自己的 UAP 调查机构，即全域异常解决办公室 (AARO)。</p><p>将在听证会上作证的三名证人之一是大卫·格鲁什（David Grusch）。这位前情报官员最近<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://thedebrief.org/intelligence-officials-say-u-s-has-retrieved-non-human-craft/">声称</a>，美国政府几十年来一直在寻找外星飞船和UAP飞行员的尸体。格鲁施在 2022 年 7 月之前一直担任国家地理空间情报局 UAP 分析的联合负责人，他还<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://nymag.com/intelligencer/2023/06/the-ufo-whistleblower-is-back-with-more-crazy-claims.html">表示</a>，有证据表明不明飞行物存在“恶意活动”。他没有提供任何物证，但他的主张导致了听证会。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/how-to-watch-this-weeks-congressional-ufo-hearing-164546251.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/how-to-watch-this-weeks-congressional-ufo-hearing-164546251.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9f255c74-c0f0-4b39-902d-86aff3a5c772</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jul 2023 16:45:46 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690303014</ingested><modified> 2023-07-25T16:37:02+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Politics & Government]]></category><category><![CDATA[Government Agencies]]></category><category><![CDATA[Government]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1971" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/bf594920-2b03-11ee-9fbe-219331b938f2" width="2987"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:conte